ssociation for Aerosol Research.</ce:para></abstract></dc:description><link href="https://api.elsevier.com/content/abstract/scopus_id/85055184814" rel="self"/><link href="https://www.scopus.com/inward/record.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&amp;scp=85055184814&amp;origin=inward" rel="scopus"/><link href="https://www.scopus.com/inward/citedby.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&amp;scp=85055184814&amp;origin=inward" rel="scopus-citedby"/></coredata><affiliation id="60027950" href="https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/60027950"><affilname>Carnegie Mellon University</affilname><affiliation-city>Pittsburgh</affiliation-city><affiliation-country>United States</affiliation-country></affiliation><affiliation id="60031155" href="https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/60031155"><affilname>Panepistimion Patron</affilname><affiliation-city>Patra</affiliation-city><affiliation-country>Greece</affiliation-country></affiliation><affiliation id="60024632" href="https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/60024632"><affilname>RJ Lee Group, Inc.</affilname><affiliation-city>Monroeville</affiliation-city><affiliation-country>United States</affiliation-country></affiliation><affiliation id="60022430" href="https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/60022430"><affilname>Institute of Chemical Engineering and High Temperature Chemical Processes</affilname><affiliation-city>Patra</affiliation-city><affiliation-country>Greece</affiliation-country></affiliation><authors><author seq="1" auid="55842167400"><ce:initials>A.</ce:initials><ce:indexed-name>Tasoglou A.</ce:indexed-name><ce:surname>Tasoglou</ce:surname><ce:given-name>Antonios</ce:given-name><preferred-name><ce:initials>A.</ce:initials><ce:indexed-name>Tasoglou A.</ce:indexed-name><ce:surname>Tasoglou</ce:surname><ce:given-name>Antonios</ce:given-name></preferred-name><author-url>https://api.elsevier.com/content/author/author_id/55842167400</author-url><affiliation id="60027950" h